Introduction

WSG Wannabe was a South Korean project girl group created on the show Hangout with Yoo as the would be the woman counterpart of MSG Wannabe. WSG Wannabe lineup consists of 12 members: Yoon Eun-hye, Navi, Lee Bo-ram, Kota of Sunny Hill, Park Jin-joo, Jo Hyun-ah of Urban Zakapa, Sole, Soyeon of Laboum, Uhm Ji-Yoon, Kwon Jin-ah, Hynn, and Jung Ji-so.
